channel.title: What was the first project you created in Auxy?
channel.description:
Auxy's iOS revision came out in June 2016. Curious to see what your guys's first project sounds like. It'll be interesting to see how much people grow in Auxy.
https://app.auxy.co/projects/HPoftXHBHE43-XNbni6Iyw== Here's mine
_First song that's posted with iPhone Auxy was this:_ https://soundcloud.com/azureonyx/planet-trance-lemonspy

item.title: What was the first project you created in Auxy?
item.dc:creator: TheRealJFalc
item.description:
I was messing with the original auxy as well as the current version for the longest of time but I never ended up making a project or song from it, except about 6 or 7 months ago I created what was probably my first song to ever be ‚Äúcomplete‚Äù in Auxy, this was when there were only two soundpacks. I hadn‚Äôt published it to soundcloud until now as it was rather‚Ä¶ bad in my opinion.
https://soundcloud.com/james-lucien-599345499/tw

However, looking back at the song now I remixed it. Since it was before automations, I used it to clean up parts of the song and added in another part or two to it, increased the tempo and raised the pitch a half step. Overall I feel it is much better now.
https://soundcloud.com/james-lucien-599345499/t-w

Not even sure why I had called it TW in the first place, but looking through my dropbox that was the name it was under so I just stuck with that. xD
